If I have some notation like this:

{code}
[!Dedicated Hosting^dedicated-hosting.png|align=right!|Dedicated Hosting]
{code}

And the page it's on is in the CPE space, then I move to the Host space, the notation ends up looking like this:

{code}
[!Dedicated Hosting^dedicated-hosting.png|CPE:align=right!|Dedicated Hosting]
{code}

Note the insertion of the old space key before align property. It's only a minor bug but really annoying when I have to go through herds of pages to edit out the unwanted space key ;)

