Either provide an option on remove page API to totally remove the page from the system or an API to remove a page from trash or both :)

We are automating creating a large number of pages (a few hundred or so) on a regular bases and then deleting them after a certain period of time.  We do not want these pages in the trash.
It would also be useful to write automation to regularly scan through the trash and delete things older than some specific date, or to archive the data somewhere. For that, we need ability to list pages from the trash.

